headline: Prediction: After Crushing the Market in 2024, United Rentals Could Have Another Winning Year in 2025
summary: Names like Nvidia and Tesla may be exciting to follow, but a quiet, industrial stock like United Rentals (NYSE: URI) can provide market-beating returns, too.  United Rentals is the industry leader with more than 1,600 global branch locations.  Shares have soared this year as United Rentals' business continues to grow.
